description: Redevelopment of the site to provide a new four storey building housing 52 extra care residential units (Use Class C3) comprising a mix of 44 x 1 bed and 8 x 2 bed units with ancillary features for use by residents including restaurant, communal lounge, activity area, IT suite, staff areas, storage, energy centre, refuse/recycling area, vehicle parking (including disabled spaces), cycle/buggy parking and associated landscaping including communal gardens and balconies
